<section id="hero" class="pt-40 pb-24 px-6 bg-ink">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="font-label text-azure-deep text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
        For online fitness coaches
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-display text-text leading-[1.05] mb-6 text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw+1.25rem,4.25rem)]">
        The AI version of you.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-text-soft text-[16.5px] md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-lg">
        One 30-minute interview becomes an AI that coaches your clients that sounds exactly like
        you, the check-ins, the DMs, the everyday stuff. No content library required.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <a
          href="#early-access"
          class="inline-block bg-azure-deep hover:bg-azure-deep/90 text-white font-semibold text-base px-7 py-3.5 rounded-md transition-colors"
        >
          Get early access
        </a>
        <a
          href="#how-it-works"
          class="inline-block text-text hover:text-azure-deep font-semibold text-base px-2 py-3.5 transition-colors"
        >
          See how it works
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-10 gap-y-4 border-t border-hairline-dark pt-8">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-text text-2xl leading-none mb-1">30 min</p>
          <p class="text-text-soft text-sm">One interview, no setup week</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-text text-2xl leading-none mb-1">24/7</p>
          <p class="text-text-soft text-sm">That sounds exactly like you, on your rules</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="bg-surface-1 border border-hairline-dark rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-3.5 border-b border-hairline-dark bg-surface-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-azure"></span>
          <p class="font-label text-text-soft text-xs">
            Sarah&rsquo;s AI &middot; replying to a client &middot; now
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-5 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="flex justify-end">
            <div class="bg-azure-deep text-white text-sm leading-relaxed rounded-2xl rounded-tr-sm px-4 py-3 max-w-[85%]">
              Stuck in a hotel this weekend, only dumbbells in the gym. Can I still get today&rsquo;s
              session in?
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-start">
            <div class="bg-surface-2 text-text text-sm leading-relaxed rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm px-4 py-3 max-w-[85%]">
              Totally. I&rsquo;ll swap you to today&rsquo;s push day with just dumbbells. Same
              intent, same effort. Sending it over now. Hit me after and tell me how the
              shoulders felt.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="font-label text-text-soft text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-center mt-4">
        in their words, on their rules
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
